nusri.fyp.demo.state_machine

Packages that use nusri.fyp.demo.state_machine
Package
Description
nusri.fyp.demo.converter
This package provides classes for converting between different data types or representations, such as converting DTOs to entities or vice versa.
nusri.fyp.demo.dto
This package contains Data Transfer Object (DTO) classes used for transferring data between different layers of the application, such as between controllers and services.
nusri.fyp.demo.entity
This package defines the entity classes used to model the data within the system.
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity.workflow
This package defines the classes related to the workflows within the Roboflow system.
nusri.fyp.demo.service
This package contains the service classes that handle the business logic of the application.
nusri.fyp.demo.service.img_sender
This package contains the image sender services responsible for sending images to external systems like Roboflow or other image processing APIs.
nusri.fyp.demo.service.img_sender.eoid
This package contains the services related to the EOID (presumably an external image data service or system).
nusri.fyp.demo.service.img_sender.roboflow
This package provides the implementation of services responsible for interacting with the Roboflow API to send images and retrieve results.
nusri.fyp.demo.state_machine
This package contains classes related to the state machine functionality, which manages the flow of the application by processing actions and transitions.
